go.wde

(W)indows, (d)rawing and (e)vents for Go.

SETUP:

To setup this project on Works on linux and windows, run the following commands (you may need to run them as root):

go get github.com/skelterjohn/go.wde
go get github.com/BurntSushi/xgbutil
go get code.google.com/p/freetype-go/freetype
go get code.google.com/p/graphics-go/graphics

If you get an error like "exec: "hg": executable file not found in $PATH", you need to install mercurial.

To enable on os x, you must first install gomacdraw.framework. There is an installer located in go.wde/cocoa/framework/gomacdraw.pkg.

